main_body:
The 1 650 000 tonnes of cereals constituting the minimum quantity to be contributed annually by the Community and the Member States under the Food Aid Convention shall be apportioned between Community and national actions for the period 1 July 1983 to 30 June 1986 as follows:
(a) Community actions: 927 663 tonnes (56 %);
(b) national actions: 722 337 tonnes (44 %).
